data.description:
LOCATION LOCATION LOCATION!!
Nestled near Moon Valley and a short hop from Desert Ridge, this property's pluses are many. Expansive owners ensuite oversized guest rooms and a spacious floorplan that includes a loft, and two living and dining spaces. Upgraded stainless appliances, sparkling PebbleTec pool, 2-car garage, & a chef's kitchen. Endless storage and hard flooring throughout leaves only one thing left, and that's for you to call it home. ALL APPLIANCES INCLUDED. FREE 1-Yr home warranty to buyer, and a Designer at your disposal for any personalization you want after purchase - at a reduced cost of course. DON'T WAIT FOR MULTIPLE OFFERS, MAKE YOURS TODAY! Seller will consider concessions. Tons of storage throughout the house. Lots of cabinets, in kitchen including pantry, multiple coat closets and storage closets and lots of space to store in garage. Spacious powder room on first floor. Spacious utility room has a doggy door. Owner currently has added a doggie door in family room slider but it's removable. Vaulted ceilings on main floor and high ceilings upstairs. Open loft is great place for kiddos to hangout and do homework. Organic interior color palette makes it easy to put your own style on this home. Refrigerator is only a few years old and conveys with house. Pool pump is high powered and works well. Water heater replaced a few years ago. Main guest bedroom is very spacious. Owners suite is very spacious with separate water closet and walk-in closet.
